Stay behind the line.

11:35.528 --> 11:37.029
[TOY SQUEAKS]

11:39.031 --> 11:40.532
Okay, mister, that's it.

11:40.533 --> 11:41.533
I'm closing.
You're a ringer.

11:41.534 --> 11:43.034
What?

11:43.035 --> 11:43.935
You're a pro, a hustler.

11:43.936 --> 11:45.437
I'll take three more balls.

11:45.438 --> 11:46.938
Hey, pal, I told you,
I'm closing.

11:46.939 --> 11:48.440
You can't close.

11:48.441 --> 11:50.442
Article two, paragraph one
of the Carnival Act,

11:50.443 --> 11:52.944
and I quote: "As long as
you got prizes and patrons,

11:52.945 --> 11:54.946
you gotta let 'em play."

11:54.947 --> 11:55.948
Really?
Yeah.

11:56.949 --> 11:59.951
You're wiping me out, pal.
What do you want from me?

11:59.952 --> 12:01.886
Look, I told you,
I'm not leaving

12:01.887 --> 12:03.388
till I get a little information.

12:03.389 --> 12:05.356
Jodie, Jodie, this is Fluffy,

12:05.357 --> 12:07.358
the carnival's
half man, half dog.

12:07.359 --> 12:10.361
He responded when I showed him
the picture of Carol.

12:10.362 --> 12:12.864
[BARKING AND PANTING]

12:12.865 --> 12:14.365
You know her?

12:14.366 --> 12:16.367
[BARKS EXCITEDLY]

12:16.368 --> 12:18.370
I think you're supposed
to give him a treat.

12:19.872 --> 12:21.372
You know this girl?

12:21.373 --> 12:23.374
Have you seen her lately?

12:23.375 --> 12:25.877
Here, here, give him that.

12:25.878 --> 12:26.879
Give it to him.

12:31.584 --> 12:33.652
[YELPS]

12:35.154 --> 12:36.654
What was that?

12:36.655 --> 12:37.655
Certs.

12:37.656 --> 12:40.158
You give a dog Certs?

12:40.159 --> 12:43.561
What, I'm supposed to carry
around a box of Liver Snaps?

12:43.562 --> 12:45.964
[GROWLS]

12:45.965 --> 12:48.967
Hey, hey, hey, hey,
are you talking to me?

12:48.968 --> 12:51.970
Listen, listen, boy,
you wanna fetch?

12:51.971 --> 12:52.971
You want to fetch?

12:52.972 --> 12:54.472
You want to fetch?

12:54.473 --> 12:56.475
Listen, tell me where
the girl in the picture is.

13:00.479 --> 13:02.480
She's in China.

13:02.481 --> 13:04.983
Look, Maggie,
this isn't gonna work out.

13:04.984 --> 13:05.984
I don't think so.

13:05.985 --> 13:07.485
Listen, uh, thanks
for your time, huh?

13:07.486 --> 13:08.987
Here ya go, here ya go, boy.

13:09.989 --> 13:12.490
All right, listen,
three more balls. Let's go.

13:12.491 --> 13:13.491
Come on, go pitch baseballs.

13:13.492 --> 13:15.460
They got some new
teddy bears in there today.

13:15.461 --> 13:18.897
I told you, I'm not leaving
till I get a little information.

13:18.898 --> 13:21.833
But don't you understand?
I'm a carnie. We live by a code.

13:21.834 --> 13:23.268
You could burn my eyes out.

13:23.269 --> 13:25.737
You could stick my head under
water. You could even audit me,

13:25.738 --> 13:26.738
but I'll never talk.

13:26.739 --> 13:29.174
How about if I give you
your dolls back?

13:29.175 --> 13:30.175
What do you wanna know?

13:30.176 --> 13:32.610
Look at the picture.
Do you know this girl?

13:32.611 --> 13:35.613
Maybe I do, and maybe I don't.

13:35.614 --> 13:37.615
Look pal, I don't give a damn
about your code.

13:37.616 --> 13:39.617
